{
  "stem": "15396.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He read in a newspaper about it, and so he came to see me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the British published something about it, and you know, they were-- at that time, the British were looking for an excuse to publicize an American in the RAF, so I got a lot of publicity that I didn't-- I wonder who are they talking about?",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A lot of the-- a lot of newspaper articles [INAUDIBLE] I think, I wonder who they're thinking, who they're talking about.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not the slightest idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not the slightest idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, but you know, once it was over, it was just a memory, and it was for us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, we never thought about-- as I say, none of my friends knew this, including my wife.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But when this Holocaust museum opened, I mean, a lot of people [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have a lot of Jewish friends being in the film business and all, and-- and you can't believe what some of the things they-- they say and some of the things they've written about me since, and all.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was about I guess 19 then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, maybe 20.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I heard about this Dr.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Gilbert and Webb, doctors who had invented a very revolutionary-- pneumothorax, but a special one, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it meant that you could get back into action even with tuberculosis, which closes the lung down, which I did.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and it actually saved my life, of course.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so I went to Colorado Springs where they were, and stayed in the hospital there for a while, and then again, I left, and then eventually got back in an ambulance corps and went back to Europe.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The American Field Service.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went back with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
